{"id": "1464258757398630696", "channel_id": "1454674789036720138", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "● 修复了「相位对弈」中唤醒体「卡斯托尔」在时释放狂气爆发显示获得卡牌「黑羽」数量异常翻倍的问题。", "timestamp": "2026-01-23T14:01:32.376000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1454674789036720138", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」回放bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1464088272975429672", "channel_id": "1463953305528176721", "type": 0, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "The jellyfish's effect shouldn't be changed like this. Drawing three cards seems great, but it actually clogs your hand.\nA natural English rendering would be:\nHaving Dimensional Image grants a gland when defending. This can lead to a situation where drawing three cards and ending up with three glands in your hand causes an overload.\nIt would be better to change it to be like Delusional Murphy, where both attacking and defending let you draw one gland into your hand (once per turn).", "timestamp": "2026-01-23T02:44:05.722000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1463953305528176721", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Swap Aigis and Aurita Absolute Axiom", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
